How hard would it be to get all of these uploaded with each half-episode in separate files?
It wouldn't be too hard to split them, I suppose. Maybe when the season is finished I'll upload a pack that's split instead of in the iTunes format if there's demand for it.

I have split the first few and removed intro and credits to make using them in XBMC less of a hassle. I'm just thinking there are probably several people that are in the same position and don't have the time to do it themselves.

If this could be done you'd be my hero.

Well, if it's for XBMC (I'm using it too) you can use a program like Media Companion to basically combine the episode info for the two parts into the same format I have the episodes in now. It'll output the video scrape info into an NFO file that XBMC will read from. I can upload the NFO files with the next torrent for XBMC users.
